<p>Van Gogh had copied texts, including poems by <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_654">Heine</rs> and <rs xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" type="person" ref="bio.xml#_841">Uhland</rs>, into two little books for Theo. See Pabst 1988, pp. 33-36.</p>
